Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:51.43,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:55.85,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Not Yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:55.85,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Not Yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.85,0:22:57.48,sign_32988_344_Cup_o__Magic_Noo,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Cup o' {\c&H5653CA&}Magic {\c&H6DFAFA&}Noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.79,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats eating a Cup o' Magic Noodles\N while everyone else is fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:07.49,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,But... Tsk, tsk, tsk. \NIt's too early to eat them yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:12.37,sign_33267_347_Magic_in_3_Minut,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Magic in 3 Minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:12.37,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,They won't be ready until three \Nminutes after you pour the magic in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:14.20,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Ladros, is it time yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:14.20,sign_33384_349_Cup_o__Magic_Noo,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Cup o' {\c&H5653CA&}Magic {\c&H6DFAFA&}Noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:16.61,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:18.45,sign_33428_350_Cup_o_Magic_Nood,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Cup o' {\c&H5653CA&}Magic {\c&H6DFAFA&}Noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:18.45,sign_33428_351_Cup_o_Magic_Nood,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Cup o' {\c&H5653CA&}Magic {\c&H6DFAFA&}Noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:18.45,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,But I like my noodles a little firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:20.09,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:21.05,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.05,0:23:21.87,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.87,0:23:23.63,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,I can do what I want—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:23.63,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.13,top,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:26.38,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:28.65,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet! Not yet! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:30.88,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,And they're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:34.08,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:34.89,main,Mars,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.53,main,Ladros,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.52,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad your arms are better now, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:43.21,main,Firnal,0000,0000,0000,,But the Queen of Witches is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.21,0:23:45.19,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Scary, but get a good look\N at her, and she's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I guess older ladies can be charming, too.
